Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？ 你剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我不去美國留學了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再聊下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當電影導演不是你的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個蠢弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.84,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,再過一陣就不能在這吃午飯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.18,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻 畫那邊進展的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒畫了還有點不適應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像找回些感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 又變回平時的美櫻了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 小夏 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻好不容易才恢復過來 可是春輝那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝他今天也沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天已經是第三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹澤他到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還有優他們去聯絡他也沒個反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 難道是因為已經決定留學了所以乾脆不來上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝肯定明天就會一臉淡定地來上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻只要專心把畫完成就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 加油哦 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝他…果然是在因為結尾那一幕發愁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟還要準備留學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為想不出好的鏡頭正在焦慮著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句話都不說就曠課什麼的 一點都不像春輝的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼辦才好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許現在的確很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙一定能拍出很棒的結尾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望太你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣 我們就相信導演然後等待他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過又要重新安排日程表了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 隨時為春輝的歸來做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就先把能做的地方都做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝 我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家訪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨戶口和望月很擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業作品你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不在也能完成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想要乾脆拋棄電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道千秋還在的話會怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部攝像機也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你說想要拍電影 千秋才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能還回去的話我也想還啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝 你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時你對千秋說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在河裡救起那個女孩子之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在病房裡說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今年也沒去給千秋掃墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然知道你不願意承認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋哥根本就不在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說夠了沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋忌日那天 去給他掃墓的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有合田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和合田好好聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明智老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能稍微佔用您一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在正在畫一幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就能畫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要拿去給春輝看 然後告訴他當年那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很後悔 之前曾經拜託明智老師不要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得合田妳很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去見春輝的時候 能幫我把這個交給他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說不想去留學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼執著地追尋著他哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是卻忘記了最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了那個的話一定能讓他想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 希望合田也能一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓春輝看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把思緒包含在一筆一劃之中的這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有此時此刻的我才能畫出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓他看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還說這些幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和合田好好聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 請不要再和我說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.93,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,由於本次冷鋒的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:18.10,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,關東地區將會迎來高於歷年11月水平的大規模降雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.35,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,本次降雪 將會於明日…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳站在這麼大雪裡幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是不來妳難道要一直等下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些話 無論如何都想告訴你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明之前那麼躲著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河裡救的那個女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天的時候我不是說過要去見恩人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他救了我之後 一直沒有見過面…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道對方是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本想著終於…終於能夠見到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於 可以向他道謝了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他卻已經過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那個人還是春輝的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果春輝知道了這件事的話 會變成什麼樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直想著 不告訴你不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一直沉默至今…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是妳躲著我的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是在搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是覺得 如果我知道了的話 會生妳的氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳該不會又想著什麼「都怪我」之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是因為自己對美櫻做了什麼過分的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以被妳討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直苦惱著啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 這種事為什麼不早點告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不用察覺到那件事了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去拍電影不是我想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝的夢想不是電影導演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是秋哥的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…一直沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一味地在模仿著秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止獲的獎 還有去美國留學的機會都不屬於我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 都是秋哥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…你才要放棄去留學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲哥告訴妳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後我也不會再拍電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可以 這麼輕易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕易？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳覺得很隨便是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也嘗試過無數次去拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無數次 無數次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不到了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拍的電影…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取景框的那一邊一片漆黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經搞不懂了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就算去了美國 也沒什麼意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就根本沒有才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓我一直拍得都是「秋哥可能想看」的鏡頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是秋哥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋哥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋哥的話…什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道去模仿秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧我有臉說自己的夢想是當電影導演啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 像白癡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電影導演是春輝的夢想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在那秋哥秋哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝滿腦子都是哥哥的事 根本就不瞭解你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在看著所以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍電影時的春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的特別開心 閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是模仿別人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會露出那樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 那可能是你哥哥的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那為什麼就不可以也是春輝的夢想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然遲交了這麼久…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就是我的 戀愛的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的 初戀的畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是 美櫻眼中戀愛的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為春輝的哥哥救了我 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能和春輝相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才有機會畫這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能夠把畫畫當做夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是多虧了你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥他也幫你找到了夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以放棄電影 放棄留學什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許你再說那種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天我爸媽回來的晚 沒辦法準備什麼像樣的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,明智老師說要把這個交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋哥的字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝 在錄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 錄著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可以了哦 秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 再靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意角度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲 你也趕快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是幹這種事的時候嗎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救了個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那你掉到河裡去是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 是為了去救溺水的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…秋哥救了美櫻那天拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.05,Default-1,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厲害啊 秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在可是拍下了最棒的一幕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的一幕？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男子漢做成一件事之後的 最棒的瞬間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 春輝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂電影 就是把最棒的每一瞬間 每一幕 每一節交織在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝 你有一直堅持去拍那些最棒的鏡頭的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我將來可是要去當導演的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當上導演 然後去拍好多厲害的電影 拿好多獎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍出能讓大家都露出笑容的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 春輝的話 一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 真敢說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把這段錄像做成DVD吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是從這一刻開始的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲 抱歉 幫我拿一下相機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 秋哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春輝的哥哥 謝謝您  y-10 x-24
